de: First Amendment to the Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Kosovo represented by the Prime Minister and the Government of the Swiss Confederation represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation concerning the Support to the Inter-Ministerial Water Council (2nd Phase of the Water Task Force)  - 06-12-2017 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Kosovo betreffend die Unterstützung für das Inter-Ministerial Water Council
en: First Amendment to the Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Kosovo represented by the Prime Minister and the Government of the Swiss Confederation represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation concerning the Support to the Inter-Ministerial Water Council (2nd Phase of the Water Task Force)  - 06-12-2017 - Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Kosovo represented by the Prime Minister and the Government of the Swiss Confederation represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs concerning the Support to the Inter-Ministerial Water Council (2nd Phase of the Water Task Force)
